# TanStack MobX Adapter

Use `@tanstack/form-core` as the engine. Do not fork it, monkey-patch it, or
replace it with a custom form engine. The adapter should bridge
`store.get()` plus `store.subscribe()` into MobX observables and expose a clean
MobX-reactive public API.

Do not make consumers subscribe to TanStack stores. Do not expose raw TanStack
state as the primary API.
